{"prompt": "Build a website for a local bookstore. The theme should be cozy and incorporate a creamy yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>The Cozy Corner Bookstore</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #FAF0E6; /* Creamy Yellow */\n            color: #5A4A3E; /* Darker brown for text */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #FFF8DC; /* Lighter creamy yellow for content */\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #FAF0E6; /* Creamy Yellow */\n            color: #5A4A3E;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #D2B48C; /* Tan border */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n        nav a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #8B4513; /* Saddle Brown */\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #5A4A3E; /* Darker brown on hover */\n        }\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #FFF8DC; /* Lighter creamy yellow */\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n        section h2 {\n            color: #8B4513; /* Saddle Brown */\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #D2B48C; /* Tan border */\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .book-list img {\n            width: 150px;\n            height: 220px;\n            margin-right: 20px;\n            border: 3px solid #D2B48C; /* Tan border */\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            float: left;\n        }\n        .book-list::after {\n            content: \"\";\n            display: table;\n            clear: both;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: #FAF0E6; /* Creamy Yellow */\n            color: #5A4A3E;\n            border-top: 2px solid #D2B48C; /* Tan border */\n        }\n        #contact-form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n        #contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #D2B48C;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #FFF8DC;\n        }\n        #contact-form button {\n            background-color: #8B4513; /* Saddle Brown */\n            color: white;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        #contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #5A4A3E; /* Darker brown on hover */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>The Cozy Corner Bookstore</h1>\n        <nav>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#books\">Our Books</a>\n            <a href=\"#events\">Events</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>A Haven for Book Lovers</h2>\n            <p>\n                Welcome to The Cozy Corner Bookstore, your local escape into the world of literature. Nestled in the heart of our community, we offer a curated selection of new and gently used books, from timeless classics to the latest bestsellers. Our warm and inviting atmosphere is the perfect place to browse, discover your next great read, and enjoy a quiet moment with a cup of tea.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                We believe in the power of stories to connect us and enrich our lives. Come find your next adventure within our pages.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"books\">\n            <h2>Featured Selections</h2>\n            <div class=\"book-list\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150x220/D2B48C/FFFFFF?text=Classic+Novel\" alt=\"Book Cover\">\n                <h3>The Great Gatsby</h3>\n                <p>A timeless tale of the American Dream.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"book-list\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150x220/D2B48C/FFFFFF?text=Fantasy+Adventure\" alt=\"Book Cover\">\n                <h3>The Hobbit</h3>\n                <p>An epic journey of a hobbit and a dragon.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"book-list\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/150x220/D2B48C/FFFFFF?text=Modern+Fiction\" alt=\"Book Cover\">\n                <h3>Where the Crawdads Sing</h3>\n                <p>A story of mystery and nature.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"events\">\n            <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>\n            <p>Join us for our monthly book club meetings, author signings, and cozy reading nights. Check back often for updates!</p>\n            <ul>\n                <li><strong>May 15th:</strong> Local Author Spotlight: Jane Doe</li>\n                <li><strong>June 10th:</strong> Summer Reading Kick-off</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Visit or Contact Us</h2>\n            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Bookworm Lane, Storyville, ST 54321</p>\n            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n            <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Monday - Saturday: 10 AM - 7 PM | Sunday: 12 PM - 5 PM</p>\n\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <h3>Send Us a Message</h3>\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 The Cozy Corner Bookstore. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}